      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable workhorse with a little TLC? This vehicle has seen plenty of life and definitely shows its age with some significant wear and tear, but it\u2019s ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a fixer-upper! It's a great opportunity to get into a vehicle at a fraction of the cost if you're handy with repairs. Sold as-is, it's the perfect canvas for your next automotive restoration project!",
