      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute beauty. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it practically still has that new car smell! Seriously, it\u2019s been pampered since day one, always kept in the garage, and there isn't a single blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream\u2014smooth, quiet, and super reliable. If you're looking for a ride that feels and looks brand new without the dealership hassle, you've found it! I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see just how gorgeous it is in person. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
