      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered platform, maintained to a rigorous standard. The high-revving 3.2L power plant features a fully serviced double-VANOS system and pristine individual throttle bodies for immediate transient response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise ZF 6-speed manual and a limited-slip variable M differential. Notably, the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure long-term structural integrity. With factory-spec suspension geometry and an interior free of bolster wear or dash UV damage, this vehicle offers a factory-fresh driving experience for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
