    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2019 BMW M2 Competition is a true collector\u2019s specimen, presented in impeccable showroom condition. Finished in Hockenheim Silver Metallic, the paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like gloss, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or scratches to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'day one' state; the Black Dakota leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the factory scent still lingers. Every surface, from the carbon fiber trim to the Alcantara steering wheel, is pristine and free of oils or wear. Mechanically, this vehicle is perfect. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized BMW centers, with a comprehensive binder of records included. The engine bay is meticulously clean, and the car has been stored in a climate-controlled garage, never seeing rain or inclement weather. It sits on its original 788M Y-spoke wheels, which are entirely free of curb rash, wrapped in a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that has been pampered and preserved to the highest possible standard.",
